name: AGUACATE SKY
description:
When the sky changes color, wild avocados appear to convert to other avocados. Your goal is to convert avocados to full avocados, resist the red sky.

-------------------------------------

Instructions: 

W: Shoot and Jump

A: Moving Left

D: Moving Right
